---
// Artista Nina - Minimalista con efectos sutiles
---

<section id="artist-nina" class="artist-section relative min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/20 via-black to-blue-900/20 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Minimal floating elements -->
  <div class="minimal-bg absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="minimal-element minimal-dot-1"></div>
    <div class="minimal-element minimal-line-1"></div>
    <div class="minimal-element minimal-dot-2"></div>
    <div class="minimal-element minimal-line-2"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Artist Horizontal Content Wrapper -->
  <div class="artist-content-wrapper flex" style="width: 400vw;">
    
    <!-- Panel 1: Introducción -->
    <div class="artist-panel w-screen min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl">
        <div class="artist-avatar mb-8">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face" 
            alt="Nina" 
            class="w-40 h-40 mx-auto rounded-full object-cover border-4 border-blue-500 shadow-2xl"
          />
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-rye font-bold text-white mb-6">NINA</h2>
        <p class="text-2xl text-blue-300 mb-4">Maestra del Minimalismo</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Menos es más. En la elegancia de la simplicidad encuentro la verdadera esencia 
          del arte. Cada línea tiene un propósito, cada espacio vacío cuenta una historia.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Panel 2: Portfolio Principal -->
    <div class="artist-panel w-screen min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 max-w-6xl">
        <div class="artwork group minimal-frame">
          <div class="minimal-element floating-dot"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1590246814883-57c511f96c5d?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Minimalista 1" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group minimal-frame">
          <div class="minimal-element floating-line"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565058379802-bbe93b2986a5?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Minimalista 2" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group minimal-frame">
          <div class="minimal-element floating-dot"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611605698323-b1e99cfd37ea?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Minimalista 3" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group minimal-frame">
          <div class="minimal-element floating-line"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1598300042247-d088f8ab3a91?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Minimalista 4" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group minimal-frame">
          <div class="minimal-element floating-dot"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1590246814883-57c511f96c5d?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Minimalista 5" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group minimal-frame">
          <div class="minimal-element floating-line"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565058379802-bbe93b2986a5?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Minimalista 6" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Panel 3: Filosofía Minimalista -->
    <div class="artist-panel w-screen min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 max-w-6xl items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-rye font-bold text-blue-400 mb-8">Elegancia en la Simplicidad</h3>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="minimal-philosophy">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Líneas Esenciales</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Cada trazo es deliberado, eliminando lo superfluo para revelar la esencia pura del diseño.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="minimal-philosophy">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Espacios Que Respiran</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">El espacio negativo es tan importante como las líneas. Permito que el diseño respire.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="minimal-philosophy">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Elegancia Atemporal</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Diseños que trascienden las modas, permaneciendo hermosos a través del tiempo.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1598300042247-d088f8ab3a91?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Filosofía de Nina" 
            class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Panel 4: Contacto & Enfoque -->
    <div class="artist-panel w-screen min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl">
        <h3 class="text-5xl font-rye font-bold text-blue-400 mb-8">Belleza en la Simplicidad</h3>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Si valoras la elegancia sutil, la belleza que no grita sino que susurra, 
          y crees que menos puede ser infinitamente más.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-12">
          <div class="contact-info">
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Disponibilidad</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">Jueves a Lunes: 13:00 - 19:00</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">Martes y Miércoles: Creación</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Consultas personalizadas</p>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-info">
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Especialidades</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">• Fine Line</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">• Micro Tatuajes</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300">• Lettering Minimalista</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-4 text-xl font-bold rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-lg">
          Agendar con Nina
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 right-8 text-white/70 z-30">
    <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Desliza →</span>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .artist-section {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .artist-content-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    will-change: transform;
  }
  
  .artist-panel {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .minimal-frame {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  /* Elementos minimalistas de fondo */
  .minimal-element {
    position: absolute;
    opacity: 0.4;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  
  .minimal-dot-1 {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: #3b82f6;
    border-radius: 50%;
    top: 15%;
    left: 20%;
    animation: breathe 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  .minimal-line-1 {
    width: 100px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #3b82f6, transparent);
    top: 40%;
    right: 10%;
    animation: breathe 6s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }
  
  .minimal-dot-2 {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #60a5fa;
    border-radius: 50%;
    bottom: 25%;
    left: 15%;
    animation: breathe 5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  .minimal-line-2 {
    width: 80px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #60a5fa, transparent);
    bottom: 10%;
    right: 30%;
    animation: breathe 7s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }
  
  /* Elementos flotantes en el portfolio */
  .floating-dot {
    position: absolute;
    top: -5px;
    right: -5px;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    background: #3b82f6;
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.7;
    z-index: 10;
  }
  
  .floating-line {
    position: absolute;
    top: -2px;
    right: -20px;
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #3b82f6, transparent);
    opacity: 0.7;
    z-index: 10;
  }
  
  .minimal-philosophy {
    padding-left: 16px;
    border-left: 1px solid #3b82f6;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .minimal-philosophy:hover {
    border-left-width: 2px;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  
  @keyframes breathe {
    0%, 100% { 
      opacity: 0.4; 
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% { 
      opacity: 0.8; 
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }
  }
  
  /* Transiciones suaves globales */
  .artwork {
    transition: all 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
  }
  
  .artwork:hover {
    filter: brightness(1.05) contrast(1.02);
  }
</style>
